    "Model OpenLLM Arena Hard Auto* Gemma-2b 46.51 -|D| = 10K Padding 42.49 3.1 + Loss Mask 43.62 2.4 Packing 47.95 5.1 + Loss Mask 48.34 5.2 |D| = 1.6M Packing 47.14 3.9 + Loss Mask 53.80 8.8 Table 3: Performance comparison for different SFT strategies on OpenLLM and Arena-Hard-Auto*.",
    "Loss masking can be used in conjunction with both packing and padding strategies.",
